name: A Rustic Messy
description: A beautiful thing can possibly grow in no matter how nasty and dangerous a place could be. We often attach into how they look without giving any fuck about what they have been through to reach it. Like a wild flower that withers when rain is pouring and blooms perfectly when the sun comes up. One by one, petal by petal, slow but sure they grew into a beautiful, magnificent and magical creation of God's hand.
